Installation of the dependance

sudo apt-get install python-flup python-pip
sudo pip install flask
sudo pip install flask-login
sudo pip install flask-wtf
sudo pip install flask-sqlalchemy
sudo pip install restclient
sudo pip install wtforms-json
sudo pip install flask-principal
sudo pip install Flask-Babel

You need to execute the setup.py to create the database.

$ python ./setup.py

Important note, the DEBUG settings in conf.py need to be true for the moment because we use the reload system from flask in debug mode for the market.
